<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 12:57:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>堪萨斯城皇家队签署价值 30 亿美元的体育场项目合同</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/royals-hallmark-partnership-push-stadium-project-past-funding-3-billion</link><description>据知情人士透露，堪萨斯城皇家队在敲定价值超过 30 亿美元的市中心新体育场开发协议后，将继续留在密苏里州。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipH1aLOl2B8g/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/royals-hallmark-partnership-push-stadium-project-past-funding-3-billion</guid></item><item><title>比特币因对特朗普延长伊朗停火的乐观情绪而上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bitcoin-rises-on-optimism-over-trump-s-extended-iran-ceasefire</link><description>周三，在唐纳德·特朗普总统表示将延长与伊朗的停火协议后，比特币与股市一起上涨，触及 11 周新高，提振了市场信心。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ij6aESUQYi6c/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 05:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-22/bitcoin-rises-on-optimism-over-trump-s-extended-iran-ceasefire</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的循环交易黑客表明 DeFi 正在吞噬自己的尾巴</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-21/the-300-million-kelp-dao-hack-shows-defi-is-eating-its-own-tail</link><description>最初的简单收益策略很快演变成一系列相互关联的风险敞口。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijcZ0xQoZIqA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-21/the-300-million-kelp-dao-hack-shows-defi-is-eating-its-own-tail</guid></item><item><title>华尔街的加密货币野心因最新黑客攻击而受挫</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-21/wall-street-s-crypto-ambitions-dealt-a-setback-by-latest-hack</link><description>Jefferies LLC 表示，周末的黑客攻击导致一个小型加密项目损失了近 3 亿美元，并引发了最大的去中心化借贷平台 100 亿美元的挤兑，这可能会减缓华尔街对区块链技术日益增长的兴趣。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ilXwUQixixyk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-21/wall-street-s-crypto-ambitions-dealt-a-setback-by-latest-hack</guid></item><item><title>加密货币黑客事件导致顶级 DeFi 贷款机构流出 90 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/crypto-hack-sparks-9-billion-outflows-from-biggest-defi-lender</link><description>周末的一次黑客攻击导致一个鲜为人知的加密项目流失了近 3 亿美元，引发了去中心化金融投资者的信任危机，用户从 DeFi 最大的借贷平台上撤走了数十亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJi9cHiPGeM4/v1/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 10:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/crypto-hack-sparks-9-billion-outflows-from-biggest-defi-lender</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 购买了 25.4 亿美元的比特币，为 2024 年底以来的最大一笔</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/strategy-buys-2-54-billion-of-bitcoin-most-since-november-2024</link><description>Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc. 在过去 7 天内购买了 25.4 亿美元的比特币，这是这家数字资产财务公司自 2024 年 11 月以来对原始加密货币的最大一笔收购。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iGVXQX8gUByg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 12:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/strategy-buys-2-54-billion-of-bitcoin-most-since-november-2024</guid></item></channel></rss>